article.headline: Brown leads Utah State over East Tennessee State 80-65 for 11th straight victory
article.description: — Darius Brown II's 19 points helped Utah State run its win streak to 11 with an 80-65 victory over East Tennessee State on Friday night.
article.linkText: Brown leads Utah State over East Tennessee State 80-65 for 11th straight victory
article.story: LOGAN, Utah -- — Darius Brown II's 19 points helped Utah State run its win streak to 11 with an 80-65 victory over East Tennessee State on Friday night. Brown also contributed eight assists for the Aggies (12-1). Great Osobor scored 15 points while going 3 of 7 and 9 of 14 from the free throw line, and added 10 rebounds. Ian Martinez had 13 points and shot 4 of 8 from the field and 5 for 7 from the line. Jaden Seymour finished with 30 points and nine rebounds for the Buccaneers (7-5). Quimari Peterson added 20 points, four assists and two steals for East Tennessee State. In addition, Ebby Asamoah had six points. ------ The Associated Press created this story using technology provided by Data Skrive and data from Sportradar.
